first_para: Jacqueline "Jackie" Doyle-Price (born 5 August 1969) is an English Conservative Party politician who was elected Member of Parliament (MP) for Thurrock in the May 2010 general election. Born in Sheffield, she lives in Purfleet. She joined the Conservative Party in 1986, as a teenager.
